    <string name="privacy_policy_body">1. Core Principle: Data Localization\n\nAll your health data, including menstrual cycles, symptoms, and other health metrics, is stored only in the encrypted database on your device.\n\n2. Information Collected\n\nWe only process information that you manually enter into the application. No automatic data collection occurs.\n\n3. Data Encryption\n\nAll sensitive data is encrypted using SQLCipher with AES-256 encryption. The encryption key is securely stored in Android Keystore.\n\n4. No Third-Party Access\n\nWe do not use any third-party analytics, advertising, or tracking services. Your data never leaves your device.\n\n5. Data Export\n\nYou can export your data at any time in standard formats (CSV, encrypted backup). You have full control over your data.\n\n6. Data Deletion\n\nYou can delete any or all of your data at any time. Deleted data is permanently removed from the device.</string>
